Max Area of Island

We care:

How large is this component?

So:

int area = dfs(...);

maxArea = Math.max(maxArea, area);

A Very Important Pattern

You are starting to see something powerful:

DFS can return information
void dfs(...)

→ Visit component

int dfs(...)

→ Return size

boolean dfs(...)

Return validity

String dfs(...)

→ Return shape/signature

This idea appears everywhere in Graphs, Trees, and DP.